attributes.attribute: Special leave is a short-term leave for personal reasons.It is regulated in paragraph 616 BGB.The following special leave days are approved by the management:
Death of the spouse or child: 2 days
If reduction of overtime is requested, the number of overtime hours must be stated.
Further information regarding the application for leave is optional except when special leave is requested. In this case, a reason must be stated.
